  <li>
    <p>Try to escape the arms race dynamic. Itâ€™s difficult to recognize, because each individual step seems reasonable when considered on its own. So retreat every so often from the field of battle and observe it from above. Donâ€™t fall victim to the madness. An arms race is a succession of Pyrrhic victories, and your best bet is to steer clear. Youâ€™ll only find the good life where people arenâ€™t fighting over it</p>
